    transliteration: "taivantu niṉ aṭittāmarai cūṭiya caṅkaraṟkuk\nkaivanta tīyum, talaivanta āṟum karantateṅkē?\nmeyvanta neñciṉ allāl orukālum virakartaṅkaḷ\npoyvanta neñcil pukalaṟiyā maṭap pūṅkuyilē.",
